- To build the example, type

$ make

- To build and view (see NOTE)

$ make view

- To clean up

$ make clean

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NOTES;
 - To define a viewer, in your shell setup define  
       VIEWER=evince 
    or VIEWER="open -a Preview"
    or VIEWER=xpf

- By default you get 16x9 slides:
   \documentclass[11pt,xcolor={dvipsnames},aspectratio=169]{beamer}
   \usepackage[serif]{gabeamer}

- To get 4x3 slides:  
   \documentclass[11pt,xcolor={dvipsnames},aspectratio=43]{beamer}
   \usepackage[serif]{gabeamer43}

- Options to gabeamer.sty are "sans", "serif", "classic".
